<div class="thumbinner" style="width:272px;"><a href="/wiki/File:Deutsches_Reich_1925_b.png" class="image" title="States of Germany (1925)"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/45/Deutsches_Reich_1925_b.png/270px-Deutsches_Reich_1925_b.png" width="270" height="218" border="0" class="thumbimage" /></a>
